etter make her quit"],[8270,8416,"so I can get her out of my head."]],"14":[[91,250,"Someone pinch me."],[250,425,"Am I really staring at my enemy"],[425,617,"Felix Barnes naked?"],[729,842,"Close the door."],[1151,1338,"I meant with you on the other side of it."],[1351,1530,"I can't. I can't leave."],[1530,1647,"Why? Because you're stalking me?"],[1647,1801,"I came in here to get my shirt."],[1801,1960,"I can't leave until I get my shirt."],[1960,2152,"You're testing my patience."],[2152,2202,"Okay."],[2202,2314,"You can get your clothes"],[2314,2448,"once I'm done changing."],[2502,2602,"What are you doing?"],[2660,2748,"The door."],[2886,2944,"Oh."],[3086,3161,"It’s locked."],[3795,3953,"What does this mean?"],[3953,4154,"It means that you're trapped with me."]],"15":[[462,588,"We need to get out of here."],[588,734,"Well, the door's bolted"],[734,946,"and there's no windows, so..."],[996,1088,"You're right."],[1151,1317,"God, I hate saying that out loud."],[1388,1630,"Well, at least you finally admitted it."],[1630,1764,"Never thought I'd live to see the day."],[1764,1910,"Don't get used to it."],[1960,2102,"I wouldn't dream of it."],[2102,2206,"Nanny."],[2740,2815,"Put this on."],[2894,3128,"Is this supposed to keep me warm?"],[3128,3274,"It’s supposed to keep you covered."],[3299,3420,"So you feel comfortable."],[3557,3670,"Body heat"],[3670,3787,"is how I'm going to keep you warm."],[3787,3924,"You're joking."],[3924,4029,"What? Like it’s that bad"],[4029,4124,"being so close to me."],[4233,4316,"Seriously?"],[4316,4433,"If we wrap this around us, then"],[4533,4633,"we’ll both stay warm."],[5013,5130,"Do you think anyone's ever"],[5130,5259,"going to get us out of here?"],[5380,5568,"Probably not for a long time."],[5776,5868,"Fuck."],[5868,6010,"Her skin's so soft."],[6385,6606,"Felix, do you have a hard on?"]],"16":[[162,291,"Felix, do you have a hard on?"],[600,663,"Y-yeah."],[729,825,"I've got a hot, half naked"],[825,917,"girl pressed up against me."],[9